# 08.06 Token Economy

## Overview

The Token Economy defines how blockchain-based incentives, ownership mechanisms, and ecosystem coordination can support the growth of cmdOS.

The token model is designed to align the interests of:

- Users
- Developers
- AI Agents
- Plugin creators
- Service providers
- Ecosystem participants

The goal is not to create speculation.

The goal is to create an economic coordination layer for an AI Execution Operating System ecosystem.

Core principle:

Network Usage

↓

Economic Activity

↓

Value Creation

↓

Ecosystem Incentives

---

